{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_018uZa2xZEyuDzbLSvPrX78V","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to generate 10 realistic fake OCR recipe text files. Let me break down the requirements:\n\n1. Save to: tools/title-loop/input/{RECIPE_TITLE}.generated.24.txt\n2. FILENAME RULES:\n   - Use SPACES, not hyphens/underscores\n   - Preserve Polish diacritics\n   - Filename title must match the main title in content (case-insensitive OK)\n\n3. RECIPE MIX: ~60% English, ~40% Polish\n   - Variety of categories\n   - Mix of single-word and multi-word titles\n\n4. AVOID these recipes (already exist):\n   - ARAYES SHRAK, Smażona zielona fasolka, CHLEBEK Z WARZYWAMI I BOCZKIEM, etc. (there are many listed)\n\n5. PATTERN REQUIREMENTS:\n   - 5 files with SPILLOVER: Corrupted text from previous recipe, broken measurements/words, 40-60 lines\n   - 3 files with NARRATIVE: 3-7 lines of prose intro between title and ingredients\n   - 2 files with SIMPLE: Basic OCR noise, stray numbers, page headers, broken words\n\nFILE LENGTH: 15-60 lines (spillover 40-60)\n\nLet me plan the 10 recipes:\n1. Spillover - English dessert\n2. Spillover - Polish soup\n3. Spillover - English main\n4. Spillover - Polish bread\n5. Spillover - English salad\n6. Narrative - English appetizer\n7. Narrative - Polish main\n8. Narrative - English beverage\n9. Simple - Polish dessert\n10. Simple - English preserve\n\nLet me make sure they're different from the existing ones and have good mix of English/Polish.\n\nRecipes to create:\n1. **Lemon Blueberry Tart** (spillover) - English dessert\n\n\n2. **Barszcz Biały** (spillover) - Polish soup\n3. **Herb Roasted Cod** (spillover) - English main\n4. **Chleb Orkiszowy** (spillover) - Polish bread\n5. **Heirloom Tomato Salad** (spillover) - English salad\n6. **Caramelized Onion Tart** (narrative) - English appetizer\n7. **Gołąbki Tradycyjne** (narrative) - Polish main\n8. **G