{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01NDzebkJaJzZdU2E8epQc7S","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01QY1G4bnUaMH3CtguszVcMZ","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Herb Roasted Cod.generated.24.txt","content":"and fold the edges inward, creating a neat parcel. Place seam-side\ndown on the prepared baking sheet. Brush the exterior with egg white\nand sprinkle with sesame seeds or poppy seeds. Let rise for 15-20\nminutes before baking.\n\nBake at 220°C (425°F) for 12-15 minutes until the pastry is puffed\nand golden brown. The filling should be hot and steaming when you cut\ninto the pastry. Serve immediately with a squeeze of fresh lemon and\na dollop of sour cream or yogurt on the side. Each parcel serves one\nto two people depending on appetite.\n\nHERB ROASTED COD\n\nINGREDIENTS:\n- 4 cod fillets, 150-175g each\n- 3 tablespoons olive oil\n- 2 tablespoons fresh dill, finely chopped\n- 1 tablespoon fresh parsley, chopped\n- 1 tablespoon fresh thyme leaves\n- 2 cloves garlic, minced\n- zest of 1 lemon\n- 2 tablespoons fresh lemon juice\n- ½ teaspoon sea salt\n- ¼ teaspoon white pepper\n- 200g baby potatoes, halved\n- 150g asparagus spears\n- 2 tablespoons butter\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\n\n1. Preheat oven to 210°C (410°F). Line a large baking sheet with\nparchment paper. Arrange potatoes and asparagus on the sheet, toss\nwith 1 tablespoon olive oil, season with salt and pepper.\n\n2. Roast vegetables for 12-15 minutes until they start to soften.\n\n3. Meanwhile, combine dill, parsley, thyme, garlic, lemon zest, and\nremaining 2 tablespoons olive oil in a small bowl.\n\n4. Remove baking sheet from oven. Push vegetables to the sides and\nplace cod fillets in the center. Spoon herb mixture over each fillet.\nSqueeze lemon juice over all.\n\n5. Return to oven and roast for 10-12 minutes until cod is opaque and\nflakes easily. Dot with butter pieces and serve immediately with\nlemon wedges."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":813,"cache_read_input_tokens":104427,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":813},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c6b5fbce-18cb-479d-8d88-154976bac39e","uuid":"3c7e2832-629a-455f-81c5-3ddd3fe05bcc"}
