 in the center. Spoon herb mixture over each fillet.\nSqueeze lemon juice over all.\n\n5. Return to oven and roast for 10-12 minutes until cod is opaque and\nflakes easily. Dot with butter pieces and serve immediately with\nlemon wedges.","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
