{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01EWo416V7UnLjtnhNjf6kU1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01JkbB7sMPWXY6KTfRhQMczn","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Caramelized Onion Tart.generated.24.txt","content":"CARAMELIZED ONION TART\n\nThis elegant yet simple tart celebrates the sweet, deep flavors that emerge when onions\nare slowly caramelized to golden perfection. Perfect as an appetizer at dinner parties or\nas a light lunch when paired with a simple green salad. The recipe comes from a French\nbistro tradition where humble ingredients transform into something truly special through\npatience and technique.\n\nINGREDIENTS:\n- 320g pre-made puff pastry or shortcrust pastry\n- 6 large yellow onions, thinly sliced\n- 3 tablespoons butter\n- 2 tablespoons olive oil\n- 1 teaspoon thyme leaves\n- 2 bay leaves\n- ½ teaspoon salt\n- ¼ teaspoon white pepper\n- 100g Gruyère cheese, grated\n- 2 tablespoons crème fraîche or sour cream\n- 1 egg yolk for egg wash\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\n\n1. Heat butter and olive oil in a large heavy-bottomed pan over medium\nheat. Add sliced onions, thyme, bay leaves, salt, and pepper.\n\n2. Cook gently for 40-50 minutes, stirring occasionally, until onions\nare deeply caramelized and golden brown. They should be sweet and\njammy. If they brown too quickly, reduce heat.\n\n3. Preheat oven to 200°C (400°F). Roll out pastry into a 9-inch tart\npan or onto a baking sheet, creating a ½-inch rim.\n\n4. Spread caramelized onions over the pastry base. Sprinkle Gruyère\ncheese over top. Drizzle with crème fraîche in small dollops.\n\n5. Brush pastry edges with egg yolk wash. Bake for 25-30 minutes until\npastry is golden and crispy. Cool for 5 minutes before slicing and\nserving warm or at room temperature."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":720,"cache_read_input_tokens":106797,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":720},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c6b5fbce-18cb-479d-8d88-154976bac39e","uuid":"31a07812-d987-4061-b0bf-d6d260d704f1"}
