{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_017vnj5M9rmontP3KrT5wECB","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_015YYj2m4iQ1sbtcMu6SFyJ3","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Makowiec Słodki.generated.24.txt","content":"PAGE 237\n\nRECIPES FROM GRANDM--'S KITCHEN\n\nMakowiec Słodki\n\nINGREDI3NTS:\n- 600 g flour (all-purp0se or bread flour)\n- 150 ml warm milk\n- 60 g softened butter\n- 50 g sugar\n- 1 whole egg + 1 egg yolk\n- 7 g dry yeast [or 20 g fresh yeast]\n- pinch of salt\n- zest of 1/2 lemon\n\nPOPPY SEED FILLING:\n- 300 g poppy seeds, ground\n- 150 ml milk, heated\n- 100 g sugar\n- 50 g butter\n- 2 tablespoons honey\n- 1 teaspoon vanilla extract\n- 30 g grated chocolate (op-tional)\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\n\n1. Mix warm milk, yeast, and 1 teaspoon sugar. Wait 10 minutes for\nactivation 2. Combine flour and salt in a large bowl. Create a well.\nPour yeast mixture, add egg, butter, 50g sugar, lemon zest.\n\n3. Knead 8-10 minutes until smooth. The dough should be soft but not\nsticky. Place in oiled bowl, cover, rise 60-90 min at warm temp.\n\n4. For filling: Pour hot milk over ground poppy seeds. Add sugar,\nbutter, honey, vanilla. Mix well. Let cool slightly.\n\n5. Punch down dough, roll into rectangle approximately 35x25 cm.\nSpread filling evenly.\n\n6. Roll tightly from long side into a log. Place in greased baking pan.\nCover, let rise 40-50 minutes.\n\n7. Brush with beaten egg yolk. Bake at 190°C (375°F) for 40-45 minutes\nuntil golden brown. Cool before cutting into s--ces."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":616,"cache_read_input_tokens":108999,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":616},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c6b5fbce-18cb-479d-8d88-154976bac39e","uuid":"1e9589f5-e7db-41f0-bc67-ff87e7d4344e"}
